{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "诺艾尔 第4话 复仇之鬼的末路",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": "",
        "content": [
            "要跳过此剧情吗？"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "我被释放后，\\n并没有回祖国而是留在了帝国……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "继续调查着关于\\n“幻狼佣兵团”的传闻。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "阁下是“幻狼佣兵团”的团长。\\n但不是那种会把无辜群众\\n卷入战争的人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "可是，为什么会流传着\\n那样的谣言呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "为了确认事情的真相，\\n我开始积极留意传闻。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵A",
            "context": "你听说了吗？\\n路过村落的补给部队的事。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120041_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵B",
            "context": "被持剑斗篷男袭击\\n而惨遭全灭的事吧。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120008_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "帝国兵A",
            "context": "是啊。听说还在半夜放火，\\n把整个村子都烧了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年A",
            "context": "隔着一座山的山顶上，\\n帝国兵的部队被尽数消灭了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120092_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年B",
            "context": "从附近村里拖出来领路的人\\n也被他用岩石统统砸死了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年A",
            "context": "真是的……想复仇的话，\\n只砍帝国兵不就好了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120092_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年B",
            "context": "我说，“幻狼的团长”\\n最初不是只针对帝国兵吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120019_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "青年A",
            "context": "说起来是啊。好像还听说\\n是个脸上带伤的剑术高人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "那、那个……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "嗯……原来是你啊。\\n司令部来新命令了吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "（摇头）……\\n告诉我“幻狼的团长”的……传闻。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "还是老样子。\\n斗篷男把村民卷入其中，继续复仇。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "和“幻狼佣兵团”刚全灭时\\n只盯着帝国兵部队的传闻\\n有天差地别啊，真是的。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "刚全灭时的、传闻……吗？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "嗯。最初的传闻是那人自揭脸面，\\n和帝国兵进行了交战。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "那、那个人……长、长什么样？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "据说好像脸上有伤痕，\\n是个身手了得的男人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "脸上……有伤痕。那……那个人，\\n是什么时候开始……把脸，遮住的？",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "什么时候开始把脸遮住的？\\n这么说来……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "有时遮住，有时又没遮……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "（写画）……唔，这个。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "信？我看看……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "“我听说了很多传闻，\\n然后听了刚才你说的一番话，我明白了”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "“传闻有两种。一种是\\n无差别复仇的斗篷男”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "“还有一种是，只和帝国兵为敌、\\n脸上带伤的男子”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "“两人的战斗方式截然不同，\\n难以想象是同一人所为”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "“提及滥杀无辜的传闻，\\n都有斗篷男登场”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "“提及只和帝国兵战斗的传闻，\\n就是脸上带伤的男子登场”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "“斗篷男遮住了脸，\\n但另一个是原本的面貌”",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "喂，那也就是说……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "“幻狼佣兵团”的幸存者有两个人，\\n他们分别以自己的方式\\n与帝国兵作战……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "（点头）……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "原来如此……\\n我们想当然地认为\\n进行复仇的幸存者……只有一个。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "（点头）……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120014_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "密探·男",
            "context": "你真厉害啊……\\n亏你能注意到这一点。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "（摇头）……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "比、比起这个，\\n有事……想拜托你。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "请把，误传的谣言……\\n纠、纠正过来。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "参谋",
            "context": "辛苦你了，诺艾尔。\\n关于维克托将军阁下的调查\\n就到此为止了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "参谋",
            "context": "不管这次的结果如何……\\n阁下还健在这件事\\n已经是不幸中的万幸了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "那个……“幻狼佣兵团”，\\n阁下他，成了一个人。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "参谋",
            "context": "我知道。\\n他很难继续执行王命了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "参谋",
            "context": "话虽如此，不去清除\\n扰乱帝国的原因也好。\\n算了……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "120010_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "参谋",
            "context": "把这份命令书交给阁下。\\n是回国的命令。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "是……是！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "又把，命令书……\\n撕毁了呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110307_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "维克托",
            "context": "我不会回去的。\\n不……是回不去了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110307_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "维克托",
            "context": "为了复仇，我舍弃了祖国和王命。\\n但现在我连复仇的希望都看不见……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110307_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "维克托",
            "context": "失去一切的我，\\n还有什么将来呢……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "阁、阁下……\\n并没有，失去一切……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "因为……有人在等着你回去，\\n还有部队的大家在！",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "科丝蒂小姐，也在等着你！\\n所以……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110307_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "维克托",
            "context": "诺艾尔……把这剑和刀\\n交给你的长官，告诉他们\\n“维克托已经作为复仇之鬼死去了”。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110307_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "维克托",
            "context": "然后，\\n就别再来这里了。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "怎、怎么这样……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110307_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "维克托",
            "context": "忘掉一切……追寻自由吧。\\n我也会……这么做的。别了，诺艾尔。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "想叫住他……想追上他。\\n虽然很想那么做，但我……",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110340_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "诺艾尔",
            "context": "只能眼睁睁地\\n看着阁下离开。",
            "voice_line": "",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}